        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3c0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:47:15.605+09:00">“Duke Xiao discussed strategy</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:47:27.025+09:00">with the three grandees Gongsun Yang, Gan Long, and Du Zhi present. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:47:37.875+09:00">Concerned about developments in the affairs of society,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:08.496+09:00">inquiring into the basis for rectifying the law,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:19.12+09:00">the Duke said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:14.548+09:00">seeking the way to direct the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:32.174+09:00">“Not to forget the earth and grain shrines after succeeding to authority</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:39.417+09:00">is the way of rulers. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:47.662+09:00">To strive for clarity and focus on what’s best in setting down laws</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:48:52.552+09:00">is the conduct of ministers. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:49:07.604+09:00">Now I want to change the law for the sake of order,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:49:16.101+09:00">and revise rituals to educate the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:49:45.577+09:00">but I’m afraid everyone will criticize me.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:49:57.859+09:00">“Gongsun Yang said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:50:23.791+09:00">“I have heard that</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:50:39.747+09:00">‘Nothing is achieved by acting with uncertainty;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:50:52.656+09:00">uncertain striving has no success.’ </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:51:06.675+09:00">Settle your worries about changing the law as soon as you can,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:51:20.702+09:00">and you won’t be concerned about the criticisms of the world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:51:30.645+09:00">“Now then, those who act as superior people do</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:16.575+09:00">are invariably rejected by society;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:25.855+09:00">those who think on the basis of individual knowledge</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:31.852+09:00">are inevitably criticized by the people. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:40.89+09:00">It is said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:49.29+09:00">‘The foolish are ignorant of what is already done,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:52.996+09:00">the intelligent see what has yet to occur.’ </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:53:58.928+09:00">You can’t consider initiatives with the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:54:00.589+09:00">but you can enjoy their success with them.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:55:10.866+09:00">“Guo Yan’s Rules says</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:55:27.895+09:00"> that those who discuss supreme virtue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:55:45.67+09:00">are incompatible with the commonplace;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:55:58.249+09:00">those who accomplish great works</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:56:08.76+09:00">do not plan with the masses. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:59:00.736+09:00">Law</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:59:11.026+09:00"> is a means of caring for the people;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:59:38.654+09:00">ritual</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T22:59:48.224+09:00"> is a way of facilitating affairs. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:00:03.68+09:00"> So if that’s what it takes to strengthen the nation,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:00:13.946+09:00">a sage doesn’t emulate precedents;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:00:26.349+09:00">if that’s what it takes to profit the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:00:34.251+09:00">a sage doesn’t conform to ritual.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:00:46.486+09:00">Duke Xiao said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:06.677+09:00">“Good.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:15.487+09:00">Gan Long said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:22.597+09:00">“No. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:39.304+09:00">I’ve heard</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:48.826+09:00">that a sage instructs without changing the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:01:57.045+09:00">the intelligent govern without altering the law. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:09.847+09:00">Those who instruct in accord with the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:17.177+09:00">succeed without laboring;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:26.921+09:00">when you govern based on the law,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:33.49+09:00">the officials are expert and the people are peaceful.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:43.304+09:00"> Now if you change the laws</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:49.882+09:00">and don’t follow the precedents of Qin,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:02:56.004+09:00">teaching people different rituals,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:03.389+09:00">I’m afraid everyone will criticize you. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:14.742+09:00">Please consider this carefully.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:24.638+09:00">Gongsun Yang said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:32.494+09:00">“What you’re saying</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:39.003+09:00">is conventional discourse.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:46.41+09:00"> The ordinary person takes comfort in old habits,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:03:55.427+09:00"> the scholar is immersed in what he studies. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:04:03.585+09:00">These two may occupy office and maintain the law,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:04:22.46+09:00">but they are not fit for discussion of what is beyond the law.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:05:36.356+09:00">“The Three Dynasties reigned without following the same rituals;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:05:44.483+09:00">the Five Overlords ruled without the same laws. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:05:52.866+09:00">So we know that the intelligent make laws,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:06:00.236+09:00">while the foolish are ruled by them;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:06:07.093+09:00">the worthy reform rituals,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:06:20.004+09:00">while the base stick to them. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:07:05.035+09:00">Those who stick to rituals</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:07:15.542+09:00">can’t be consulted about business;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:07:25.436+09:00"> those ruled by laws</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:07:35.568+09:00">can’t be consulted about change. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-31T23:08:05.083+09:00">Have no doubt, sir.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:35:08.514+09:00"> that you shouldn’t change the law if there’s not a hundred times the advantage to do so,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:34:41.412+09:00">Du Zhi said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:34:55.964+09:00">“I’ve heard</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:35:21.875+09:00">or replace instruments if there’s not ten times the efficiency. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:35:41.545+09:00">I’ve heard that you make no mistakes if you emulate the past,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:35:55.671+09:00">and won’t go wrong if you conform to ritual. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:36:50.487+09:00">You should strive for this, sir.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:37:09.506+09:00">“Gongsun Yang said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:37:29.174+09:00">“Former ages didn’t have the same culture—</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:37:43.159+09:00">what past should we emulate? </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:37:56.614+09:00">The emperors and kings did not follow each other—</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:38:10.642+09:00">what ritual should we conform to?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:38:27.647+09:00">“Fu Xi [who is said to have established leadership in 2857 BCE] and Shennong [who is said to have assumed leadership in 2737 BCE] admonished but did not punish. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:38:44.763+09:00">The Yellow Emperor [trad. r. 2697-2597 BCE], Yao [ trad. r. 2356-2256 BCE], and Shun [2255-2207 BCE] punished but did not get angry. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:39:03.036+09:00">Coming to Wen and Wu [12 th century BCE],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:39:17.712+09:00">each established laws for their time,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:39:22.719+09:00">and formulated rituals according to events. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:39:33.027+09:00">Ritual and law are determined according to the time,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:39:43.768+09:00">regulations and directives each follow what is appropriate,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:40:07.073+09:00">arms and equipment are each suited to their uses.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:40:37.159+09:00"> I therefore say</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:40:46.306+09:00">there is not just one way to govern society,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:41:18.004+09:00">so a nation need not emulate precedent. ”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:42:45.999+09:00">“Tang [1766 BCE] and Wu [1122 BCE]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:42:54.979+09:00">rose to kingship without following precedent;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:43:14.267+09:00"> the Yin [1766-1122 BCE] and Xia [2357-1766 BCE] dynasties perished</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:43:31.569+09:00">without changing their rites. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:43:40.472+09:00">So those who contravene precedent are not necessarily wrong,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:43:55.519+09:00">while those who conform to ritual are not altogether right. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:44:09.459+09:00">Have no doubt, sir.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:44:23.678+09:00">Duke Xiao said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:44:32.805+09:00">“Fine. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:44:44.307+09:00">I have heard that there are lots of superstitions in the slums,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:44:51.141+09:00">lots of debates among crooked scholars. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:45:03.159+09:00">What the foolish laugh at,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:45:10.903+09:00">the wise lament;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:45:27.49+09:00">what madmen delight in</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:45:35.517+09:00">troubles the conscientious. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:46:16.642+09:00">I do not hesitate to confine my deliberations to this era.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:48:24.479+09:00">With this, he promulgated a directive to cultivate unused lands.”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
